title: Ep. 538 - Dissolve Planned Parenthood
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, the Attorney General of New York is going after the NRA, seeking to dissolve it for its alleged criminal conduct. That brings up a good question: Why hasn’t any Republican AG done this with Planned Parenthood? Also Five Headlines including Joe Biden accidentally being racist again. Plus another actress issues a tearful public apology. The reason is possibly the most absurd yet.
